# Web Design Standards

For any task involving visual design, page composition, UI components, responsive behavior, interaction design, visual implementation, or visual review, load and follow `web-design-guidelines`.

Install the dependency when it is not already available:

```bash
npx skills add https://github.com/antfu/skills --skill web-design-guidelines
```

## Precedence

1. Explicit user decisions and applicable legal or professional constraints.
2. Approved spec for the active unit of work.
3. Approved Design Document.
4. Project brand guidelines, content inputs, and design tokens.
5. Repository rules and established architecture.
6. `web-design-guidelines`.
7. General framework conventions.

Do not let the external skill override approved brand, content, accessibility, privacy, legal, product, or technical decisions. Document material conflicts and follow the higher-priority source.
